You take your phone out or your iPad out.

00:15:38.570 --> 00:15:42.360
You take the turn that
you've got earlier today.

00:15:42.440 --> 00:15:47.440
And you can just have a little bit
of fun in the time that you have,

00:15:47.440 --> 00:15:47.450
put your phone away, and then you go.

00:15:48.590 --> 00:15:52.720
So let me recap exactly how
turn-based multiplayer works,

00:15:52.760 --> 00:15:56.000
and then we'll get into some of
the new features we've added.

00:15:56.080 --> 00:16:01.670
So remember, in iOS 5,
Aideen would send out the invitations,

00:16:01.670 --> 00:16:05.400
and before Bill, Claire,
and Deirdre even get the invitation,

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:07.840
