hiking out in Yosemite,

00:16:17.660 --> 00:16:20.140
so he doesn't get the notification.

00:16:20.140 --> 00:16:23.770
And in iOS 5, that's it.

00:16:23.930 --> 00:16:28.020
The game will now stand here
