you save the match data,

00:19:14.420 --> 00:19:17.510
the notification goes out
to all the participants,

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:19.240
and everything updates.

00:19:20.810 --> 00:19:22.640
So that's turn-based timeouts.

00:19:22.780 --> 00:19:26.350
And we think this is a real critical
element to preventing abandoned games.

00:19:26.470 --> 00:19:29.510
And an abandoned game, of course,
isn't a fun game.

